#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn28.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 28 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 28 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Sāriputtavagga "
msgstr "1. With Sāriputta "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Upekkhāsutta "
msgstr "4. Equanimity "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn28.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.4:1.2"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā ānando … pe … "
msgstr "Venerable Ānanda saw Venerable Sāriputta and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.4:1.3"
msgid "“vippasannāni kho te, āvuso sāriputta, indriyāni; parisuddho mukhavaṇṇo pariyodāto. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, your faculties are so very clear, and your complexion is pure and bright. "

msgctxt "sn28.4:1.4"
msgid "Katamenāyasmā sāriputto ajja vihārena vihāsī”ti? "
msgstr "What meditation were you practicing today?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn28.4:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "“Reverend, with the giving up of pleasure and pain, and the ending of former happiness and sadness, I entered and remained in the fourth absorption, without pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness. "

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "But it didn’t occur to me: "

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.3"
msgid "‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti. "
msgstr "‘I am entering the fourth absorption’ or ‘I have entered the fourth absorption’ or ‘I am emerging from the fourth absorption’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.4:2.4"
msgid "Tathā hi panāyasmato sāriputtassa dīgharattaṃ ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayā susamūhatā. "
msgstr "“That must be because Venerable Sāriputta has long ago totally eradicated ego, possessiveness, and the underlying tendency to conceit. "

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.5"
msgid "Tasmā āyasmato sāriputtassa na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "That’s why it didn’t occur to you: "

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.6"
msgid "“‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti. "
msgstr "‘I am entering the fourth absorption’ or ‘I have entered the fourth absorption’ or ‘I am emerging from the fourth absorption’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn28.4:2.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

